Lanys</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usyldane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>syldane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/21/01 4:50:10 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: HELP! -- a terribly newbish faction question =)</span><hr size=1> You mean the Inert Potion quest with the Slansin fellow downstairs in the potion shop?  That does help Corrupt Qeynos guards and FP militia also, but it takes hundreds of hits to recover from Glares to Indifferent.  Does it also help the merchants?  If by some way Slansin were to end up next to the quest giver on the 3rd floor though, you just just hot key the quest text and give the potion over and over again very quickly.  I guess if you see someone kite Slansin up to the 3rd floor and then fail to kill him, you could keep handing him potions all day, as long as you hailed him occasionally to keep him in place.  Just don't pull him up the steps, root him next to the dude that gives the potion, gate out where you bound on the steps, then zone back in to do the quest ad infinitum.  That would be exploiting I imagine.  Hmmm.  I don't suppose this method has been 'fixed' by verant since that time I found him strangely rooted by the questgiver (Torisian, I think is the name). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uadiyencrowe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Adiyen Crowe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/21/01 8:11:39 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Uhm...</span><hr size=1> What mob and where? :) And I got Slansin to spawn...FINALLY! hehehee <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uadiyencrowe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Adiyen Crowe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/1/01 6:29:21 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: HELP! -- a terribly newbish faction question =)</span><hr size=1> Ohyes and after killing that merchant, I found out she's on HHK merchant faction =)<br>
<br>
Forget that! thats a hard one to raise, gathering up ears and scalps and such.. <br>
<br>
For anyone wondering, ERUDIN sells bat wings and fish scales and everything else you may need. If your faction is bad with the caster guilds, just go kill that Elial Brook guy in Toxx a few times at the docks. Loot his Bones.<br>
<br>
Not only does killing him give a really nice faction hit, his bones can be turned in to Markus Jaevins in the caster guilds, and thats even more + faction for you.<br>
<br>
Elial Brook is really low level, spawns every 5 minutes. <br>
<br>
Anyways, I'm off =) <br>
